rows.label: tlk70000071_02_msg0001
rows.name:
It's been a long time since
I've been back, but this country
hasn't changed at all...

rows.label: tlk70000071_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The Iiran King's always had the
favor of the people, but Zettar,
the next in line, is a real arse.

rows.label: tlk70000071_02_msg0003
rows.name:
The royal heir he may be, but
the man's small-minded and only
considers his own advancement.

rows.label: tlk70000071_02_msg0004
rows.name:
In fact, he's the only one who
hasn't noticed his own behavior.
Such is his foolishness.

rows.label: tlk70000071_02_msg0005
rows.name:
So it goes with those proud types...
Maybe deep down he realizes, but
just doesn't want to admit it...
